Name: DED
About the game: DED - a game in the shoot'em up genre. Your granddaughter has been kidnapped, and your daughter and son-in-law murdered. Having just bits and pieces of information about the abductors, you will have to save your granddaughter and find the masterminds behind these crimes. A moderately hardcore game with dynamic gameplay that will help you while away a few evenings. Survival Mode FAQ.
